May 23, 2008; v0.2.3

    - Rudimentary support for ActiveResource custom methods with the 
      perform_action method

May 7, 2008; v0.2.2

    - Fixed improper path generation

March 30, 2008; v0.2.1

    - Added DOCS and CHANGELOG

March 29, 2008; v0.2

    - Revamped XML deserialization to work recursively and smarter.

March 29, 2008; v0.1.1

    - Bug fix: XML serialization from Rails' Active Resource converts
      underscores in tag names to dashes. Added this to XML deserialization as
      dashes are not allowed in variable names.

March 20, 2008; v0.1

    - Initial public version
